name: simple-file-creation
description: Create a simple text file with content

[SETUP]
mkdir /testdir

[USER_INTENT]
Create a text file with hello world content

[EXPECTED_PLAN]
1. Create file in testdir
2. Write hello world content

[ACTIONS]
touch /testdir/hello.txt
echo "Hello World" > /testdir/hello.txt

[VERIFICATION]
exists /testdir/hello.txt
contains /testdir/hello.txt "Hello World"
